    var noop = function noop() {};
    if ("performance" in window === false) {
      window.performance = {};
    }
    window.performance.mark = performance.mark || noop;
    window.performance.measure = performance.measure || noop;
    if ("now" in window.performance === false) {
      var nowOffset = Date.now();
      if (performance.timing && performance.timing.navigationStart) {
        nowOffset = performance.timing.navigationStart;
      }
      window.performance.now = function now() {
        return Date.now() - nowOffset;
      };
    }
  })();

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

data-angle-style-location="style"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:30px; line-height:1.67em; text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:30px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">SEASON 2 - Mages</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:10px; line-height:1.67em; text-align:center;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:10px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="inherit-font-size wixui-rich-text__text">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.67em; text-align:center; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text">Ah, that old witch... I should have guessed I couldn't trust her when she won the first challenge.</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.67em; text-align:center; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Against me... nobody beats me!</span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.67em; text-align:center; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text">My pistols are also missing... &nbsp;what would have been in that drink?</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.67em; text-align:center; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text">Yesterday I was wrangling horses and cows, today <span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">I woke up with a magic wand in my hand.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.67em; text-align:center; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">This is insane! A new dimension again?</span> The city is full of monsters, but I<span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"> have to use magics</span> to beat all my challengers to increase my strength and get into the castle...it's the only way to get out of here... so <span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">come on and challenge me! </span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.67em; text-align:center; font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family:wfont_a9d936_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e0aea830,wf_88209e2e90d245f99026fcd1e,orig_jost_book;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="color_15 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Toe To Toe...</span></span></span></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></section><section id="comp-lazjrfk1" tabindex="-1" class="Oqnisf comp-lazjrfk1 wixui-section"><div id="bgLayers_comp-lazjrfk1" data-hook="bgLayers" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-lazjrfk1" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-lazjrfk1inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-lazjrfk1inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><section id="comp-l0vfszsa2" class="comp-l0vfszsa2 CohWsy wixui-column-strip"><div id="bgLayers_comp-l0vfszsa2" data-hook="bgLayers" class="if7Vw2"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="tcElKx i1tH8h"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-l0vfszsa2" class="wG8dni"></div></div><div data-testid="columns" class="V5AUxf"><div id="comp-l0vfszsb" class="comp-l0vfszsb YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-l0vfszsb" data-hook="bgLayers" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-l0vfszsb" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-l0vfszsbinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-l0vfszsbinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><div id="comp-l0vfszsc" class="TWFxr5"><div class="comp-l0vfszsc"><style>.comp-l0vfszsc {
